{"lemma":"عَيّ","slug":"عَيّ","root":"ع.#.#","root_slug":"ع-_-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-_-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n31139"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31139","headword_ar":"عَىٌّ","root":"EY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayiY~N","text_ar":"عَيِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K, TA,) the former of which is the more common, (TA,) are epithets denoting the agent of the verb in the phrases"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaY~N biAlA^amori","text_ar":"عَىٌّ بِالاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaY~a Eano Huj~atihi","text_ar":"عَىَّ عَنْ حُجَّتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaY~a fiY manoTiqihi","text_ar":"عَىَّ فِى مَنْطِقِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": [i. e. they signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Unable to find the right way,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., in relation to an affair, and an argument or the like, and in the expression of his ideas; agreeably with the explanations of these phrases in the first paragraph of this art.:] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eay~aAnu","text_ar":"عَيَّانُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayaAyaA='u","text_ar":"عَيَايَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) signify the same, (S, K,) in relation to an affair and to the expression of one's ideas: (S:) the pl. [of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaY~N","text_ar":"عَىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoyaA='N","text_ar":"اَعْيَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayiY~N","text_ar":"عَيِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoyiyaA='u","text_ar":"اَعْيِيَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) Sb says, Yoo has informed us of this; and he says, we have also heard some of the Arabs say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoyiyaA='u","text_ar":"اَعْيِيَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as above] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoyiyapN","text_ar":"اَعْيِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA"]}]}}